{
  "text": "where OxyHb is the fit coefficient for oxyhemoglobin, and DeoxyHb is the fit coefficient for deoxyhemoglobin, resulting from the linear regression. [CITATION_1] The mean values for S HSI O 2 , for OxyHb, and for DeoxyHb were calculated across the entire ROI of each image at each timepoint, yielding variables which were then subjected to further statistical analysis by conventional methods (see below). In addition, grayscale images were generated in which the brightness of each pixel is proportionate to the S HSI O 2 value for that pixel. All spectral computations were done using Matlab (The Mathworks, Natick, MA).",
